    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deae Nehalen<lb break="no" n="2"/>niae <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Ariseniu<lb break="no" n="3"/>s Marius libert<lb break="no" n="4"/>us <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Ariseni V<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><lb break="no" n="5"/>hi negotiato<lb break="no" n="6"/>ris Britannicia<lb break="no" n="7"/>ni ob merces <lb n="8"/>bene cons<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>rva<lb break="no" n="9"/>ta<supplied reason="lost">s <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>4 fast aneinanderpasssende Fragmente erhalten. Auf den beiden Nebenseiten je ein Baum; auf der Oberseite zwei Äpfel. Mit freundlichem Hinweis von Marie-Thérèse Raepsaet-Charlier.</p>
            </div>
